</title>
<subSubSection id="0F2197EF21D789864A7979609B8F4BDA" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" type="description">
<paragraph id="63D04B8275295AA8537602748D723433" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="625152C01FD3AD53355EA38B18A33C86" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Jovibarba" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,IPNI" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="allionii">
<emphasis id="B997544A2E19E337ECA9FD9FE7EBA658" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">S. Allionii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 6) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="A044838E5E21BD8D8EDC6847714A95F4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<normalizedToken id="75081D2CB0296F15E19EC185BA69AE10" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
nur am Rande mit 
<normalizedToken id="42FC25943A4F40EE89953C2521B7523D" originalValue="Drüsen" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Druesen</normalizedToken>
, auf der 
<normalizedToken id="E164BE0B9E6DA045551460D5B84F9337" originalValue="Fläche" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Flaeche</normalizedToken>
kahl
</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="297F066815B97701DDE4FC9761FC5872" originalValue="übrige" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">uebrige</normalizedToken>
habituelle Unterscheidungsmerkmale haben kaum systematischen Wert!). - 
<normalizedToken id="A8462C3A033405E81CAFC53381F2B266" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="455CFA36630D12F38FDD12C37422617B" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis id="9379F5053A7E22B146ED2B857434859A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<pageBreakToken id="E21AD4E360E49FFA7A854588DC8D1ABF" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben. 2n
</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="B343F5A497F7496758DE8FE8D8F65F19" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">38:</emphasis>
Ohne Herkunftsangabe des Materials (
<normalizedToken id="EB9B290BEE73F82F553A4BA2C1B97F8C" originalValue="Zésiger" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Zesiger</normalizedToken>
1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EE27318ED597D86C98843A43555DEFA3" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis id="D87A0DEB274A76F728546EEEF047A24B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan und subalpin. Wie 
<taxonomicName id="3F16283497C99D41F8EDDC82B2EBF0E0" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Jovibarba" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,IPNI" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="allionii">
<emphasis id="1D536D2CB32BCFED65F6D1DB405E5E6B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">S. Allionii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 6).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="27154B1E942B69117CFEF37660698D13" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis id="4E0A9990F6F3B34F1C1427F75968AC1F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Verbreitung. Ostalpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
Von den Bergamasker Alpen 
<normalizedToken id="175C756B27E51F4225F55B5347AC5D17" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis in die Niederen Tauern. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel et al. (1965). - Im Gebiet: Bergamasker Alpen (Tonale, Edolo, Presolana, Gavia).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="51FA2F889399A8ECF4ADF2A311168ED4" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis id="D8E385B76A8EC70BC29C48DBD5271597" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Weitere 
<normalizedToken id="502480AAE03FCAA1F93D92EEE2C3D770" originalValue="östliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">oestliche</normalizedToken>
Sippen, die sich wohl nur habituell von 
<taxonomicName id="36677B640AA86907343218234E563C92" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Sempervivum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="arenarium">
<emphasis id="38490B0A4C58474C4E5AC18E3C253357" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">S. arenarium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
unterscheiden, sind die 
<taxonomicName id="6DDDB84480B1C1D1FE06A205D3F7801C" authority="Juslen" authorityName="Juslen" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" rank="subSpecies" subSpecies="hirtus">
ssp. 
<emphasis id="0DFDBD7CD6E2D74C5C8B3E019C56412E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">hirtus</emphasis>
Juslen
</taxonomicName>
und die 
<taxonomicName id="2E6347B165C612A934C90932AD1F876C" authority="H. Huber" authorityName="H. Huber" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" rank="subSpecies" subSpecies="borealis">
ssp. 
<emphasis id="5AAA09B407B48B831B59C5D0C22AA46A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">borealis</emphasis>
H. Huber
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="279C4BFAFADC991222922FE3B81E5723" authority="L." authorityName="L." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Sempervivum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="globiferum">
<emphasis id="6B8B055217DD9FDA7384A4FC66E45098" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">S. globiferum</emphasis>
<authorityName id="6F84F3422D89767A3495473A1E35A1DE" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">L.</authorityName>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="409C1AC7361F3A4EED7A708342358578" authority="Sims" authorityName="Sims" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Sempervivum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="soboliferum">
<emphasis id="43B894BAA76710E80793293DA7259E0E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">S. soboliferum</emphasis>
Sims
</taxonomicName>
). Siehe auch Bemerkungen unter 
<taxonomicName id="51760B2814753F782100BC13549234CD" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Jovibarba" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,IPNI" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="allionii">
<emphasis id="EB2ED745B50635ABA7F46E7549903A0C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">S. Allionii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 6).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8D2641E02BB2A5A49B06DBE1B4E4CAFA" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">
Die 4 von Huber (in Hegi 1V/2 1963) unter 
<taxonomicName id="BD6A02781173870C5AA07039D52EC778" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Sempervivum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="259" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hirtum">
<emphasis id="39F9BB486233EF632EBA039C5E7F935F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="941EDB08E359FE078387A896D3D476D8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">hirtum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
genannten Unterarten sollten experimentell auf den systematischen Wert 
<normalizedToken id="9A36FF2002A3B6A7E6C9538FBC7C3180" originalValue="geprüft" pageId="null" pageNumber="259">geprueft</normalizedToken>
werden.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
